{"tid":1248461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(數據撚)選民登記情況","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T13:32:00.000Z","uid":260929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"850aeb705e02526f1ca557c9b614a30df878b0ed","tid":1248461,"uid":260929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:52:57.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係急事,但都係擺定上蒞先<br />\ncheck 咗選舉事務處嘅選民登記資料(2018年), 發現一啲有趣現象<br />\n<br />\n1. 首先,  年輕人登記數量係真心少,同班廢老無得比:<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhEN29L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhEN29L.png&h=e4ffe9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後我再用2016年人口普查數據計吓選民登記率, 呢個因為年份同年齡組別差異唔係100%准, 但都可以參考吓:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6N0NiWQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6N0NiWQ.png&h=0e06da6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先唔好理15-20歲個group人登記比例少, 人口普查得15-20歲資料, 乘返2就係大約嘅實際比率<br />\n2. 可以見到整體蒞講年輕人嘅登記比例都係比較低, 26-30歲組別只有60%左右, <strong>30-34歲組別得50%</strong>, 而60-70歲組別就有成80%<br />\n3. 雖然唔明顯, 但<strong>女性登記比例比男性略低</strong><br />\n然後再細分5大立法會分區情況:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JqCgciS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJqCgciS.png&h=f364aebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9y9VsGQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9y9VsGQ.png&h=3748c9a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n4. 新東同九東有唔少人都登記咗做選民(70%以上), <strong>新東56-70歲組別登記率更超過90%</strong><br />\n5. 相對地, 九西同新西就比較少, <strong>九西仲要得50%, 而呢區35歲以下年輕人登記率, 只得40%<br />\n</strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yafYqw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyafYqw9.png&h=6c28d1bd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n6. 有趣嘅係, 泛民同自決派, 2016年就係喺新東同九西打嬴建制(議席數), 呢個涉及選舉工程, 就唔喺度講<br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 區選係就係遠咗啲, 但選民登記2/7就deadline,大家記得快啲登記!!!<br />\n換咗身分證嘅, 快啲上選舉事務處check資料, 唔好因為政府啲無聊bug攪到無啦啦被DQ<br />\n同埋各位發緊夢嘅朋友, 萬事小心, 兄弟爬山<br />\n<br />\n廢柴一件咩都唔識, 人脈又無, 又唔識文宣, 只能做呢啲無聊嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9eb6768d805c33d2d235037c0048dc993e8eaf","tid":1248461,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必睇!!!!!<br />\n認真, 咁多位義士<br />\n呢個係狗屋( 警察總部)<br />\n入面無野多, 狗最多, 軍火最多<br />\n再者軍火多, 你衝入去可以認為你想搶槍<br />\n實彈射擊你班友, 我唔想每年平反621<br />\n衝就一定, 但唔係狗屋<br />\n認清目標, 叫親你衝狗屋既, 一係三毛, 一係警犬, 一係有病<br />\n圍住, 守住狗屋就好足夠<br />\n唔好受任何網上/現場既人挑釁<br />\n你要守, 要挨<br />\n衝立會係唔比開會, 衝狗屋係無撚用, 佢地出唔到黎就得<br />\n有傳 狗已部署重兵4千, 前後夾擊, 一擊就夾死你地!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190621&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59743894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190621%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59743894&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=b19ef5a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190621%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59743894&h=09f88b5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190621&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59743894</a></span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9f58130a4f38d82cb4ad8e65aa8dc164a3388071","tid":1248461,"uid":80965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:32:00.000Z","msg":"登記做選民!!"}]}